18 system during a fiscal year. Annual compensation shall not include payment for any
19 benefit or salary adjustments made by the public board, institution, or agency to the
20 member or on behalf of the member which is not available as a benefit or salary
21 adjustment to other members employed by that public board, institution, or agency.
